Another week, another issue! This week the guys talk Batman #39, Tom King's writing style, and the cliffhanger that's got everyone going bananas. Are they fans of the current Batman and Catwomen relationship, or did it go over like a Kite Man origin story? The opinions are strong in this brand new episode of Major Issues! [Download](https://comicbookclique.podbean.com/mf/play/i9h9ef/MIE08.mp3)

  
